text: Stefania Krupa (14 December 1909 - 24 September 1981) was a Polish gymnast. She competed in the women's artistic team all-around event at the 1936 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1909 births Category:1981 deaths Category:Polish female artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Poland Category:Gymnasts at the 1936 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Warsaw Category:People from Warsaw Governorate
